(6903, '_transient_dash_1ba4cf213ee97a4b25c78e8a35c7da22', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2017/03/wordpress-4-7-3-security-and-maintenance-release/''>WordPress 4.7.3 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">6 Березня 2017</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.7.3 is now available. This is a security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. WordPress versions 4.7.2 and earlier are affected by six security issues: Cross-site scripting (XSS) via media file metadata.  Reported by Chris Andrè Dale, Yorick Koster, and Simon P. Briggs. Control characters can trick redirect [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://heropress.com/essays/going-back-roots/''>HeroPress: Going Back To My Roots</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/bocoup-launches-study-to-measure-impact-of-open-work-on-developer-well-being''>WPTavern: Bocoup Launches Study to Measure Impact of Open Work on Developer Well-Being</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/woocommerce-3-0-0-scheduled-for-release-april-4th''>WPTavern: WooCommerce 3.0.0 Scheduled for Release April 4th</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class="dashboard-news-plugin"><span>Популярний плагін:</span> Page Builder by SiteOrigin&nbsp;<a href="plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=9e8b694164&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800" class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="Встановити Page Builder by SiteOrigin">(Встановити)</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
